                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8268" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0236</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1939 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创造绿能世界，助力“双碳目标”－－隆基绿能ESG实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Creat a Green World to Achieve the Dual Carbon Target：ESG practice by LONGi</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏忠秦，彭昱辰，肖作平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州电子科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隆基绿能科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双碳目标；隆基绿能；ESG实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dual Carbon Target; LONGi; ESG practice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国“双碳”目标的提出，ESG理念得到了广泛的关注，同时党的二十大指出要大力发展绿色低碳产业，为ESG的发展指明了方向。“隆基绿能”致力成为太阳能产业领导者，助力人类能源变革，推动人类生态环境修复，为子孙后代创建绿色家园。“隆基绿能”的这种理念正好与ESG倡议不谋而合。本案例聚焦“隆基绿能”的ESG实践之路，描述了“隆基绿能”的可持续发展历程、ESG的实施路径和效果，旨在帮助学生深入理解ESG的内涵、驱动因素以及具体的实施策略，引导学生思考ESG理念对企业可持续发展的重要作用。与此同时，本案例还可以为企业如何构建自上而下的ESG治理架构提供借鉴，进而推动企业环境、社会、经济效益的统一，促进企业的高质量与可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the proposal of China&#39;s &quot;double carbon&quot; goal, the concept of ESG has been widely concerned, and the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China pointed out that we should vigorously develop green and low-carbon industries, which pointed out the direction for the development of ESG. LONGi is committed to being the most valuable solar technology company in the world and helping human energy revolution. Promote the restoration of human ecological environment and create a green home for future generations. This concept of LONGi coincides with the ESG initiative. This case focuses on the ESG practice of LONGi, describes the sustainable development process of LONGi, the implementation path and effect of ESG, aims to help students deeply understand the connotation, driving factors and specific implementation strategies of ESG, and guide students to think about the important role of ESG in the sustainable development of enterprises. At the same time, this case can also provide reference for enterprises how to build a top-down ESG governance structure, so as to promote the unity of environmental, social and economic benefits of enterprises and promote the high-quality and sustainable development of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论;战略性企业社会责任理论;ESG信息披露效应;信号传递理论;利益相关者理论;合法性理论;可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-04</td>
                            </tr>
